{{short description|A group of crystals formed in an open space with form determined by their internal crystal structur}}
[[Image:Quartz, Tibet.jpg|thumb|A [[quartz]] crystal cluster from [[Tibet]]]]
[[File:Calcite-Dolomite-71009.jpg|thumb|Dolomite druse (pink) with calcite crystals]]
